snippet.title: Space to Grow Visual Novel Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the sequel to Our Personal Space - Space to Grow! Available now!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1706470
itch.io: https://metasepia.itch.io/space-to-grow
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.icecavern.metasepia.spacetogrow

Download the previous game, Our Personal Space: https://www.metasepiagames.com/OurPersonalSpace/index.html
Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/MetasepiaGames

Background music "Found", by Jeff Wahl: http://magnatune.com/artists/jeff_wahl/
